into teams.

587
00:32:08,300 --> 00:32:09,910
We'll give them different garments

588
00:32:09,910 --> 00:32:10,900
to mix and match.

589
00:32:11,390 --> 00:32:12,700
This should get

590
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:14,170
the viewers coming.

591
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:16,910
Sounds like a good idea,

592
00:32:16,910 --> 00:32:19,140
but I think it needs a lot of work.

593
00:32:21,790 --> 00:32:23,290
I'm okay with it

594
00:32:23,870 --> 00:32:25,710
because I plan to spend more time

595
00:32:25,790 --> 00:32:27,010
on work.

596
00:32:27,570 --> 00:32:28,730
Don't worry, Xi Xi.

597
00:32:28,820 --> 00:32:30,410
Don't worry.
I'll help you.

598
00:32:30,630 --> 00:32:31,810
I'll help too.

599
00:32:37,420 --> 00:32:39,020
Let's quickly divide these.

600
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:42,330
Did you see that?

