604
00:32:50,910 --> 00:32:52,510
Looking at her dark circles,

605
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:55,350
people may think she's
going for the goth look.

606
00:32:55,990 --> 00:32:57,190
What happened to her?

607
00:32:57,270 --> 00:32:59,330
She only lost the CEO position.

608
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:01,620
I think she has a relationship problem.

609
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:04,490
I think so too.

610
00:33:04,580 --> 00:33:06,450
Room Two needs more light.

611
00:33:06,550 --> 00:33:08,740
Tell Tiao Tiao in Room Six

612
00:33:08,820 --> 00:33:10,580
