613
00:33:10,670 --> 00:33:12,780
Change it to the next one.

614
00:33:13,910 --> 00:33:15,780
The next flagship style.

615
00:33:18,460 --> 00:33:19,580
Pass the dress to Mr Five.

616
00:33:19,580 --> 00:33:21,980
Pass the blouse to Warm Broadcast.

617
00:33:22,690 --> 00:33:24,020
And the other blouse...

