620
00:33:28,150 --> 00:33:30,690
They're mostly fashion and cosmetic.

621
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:32,980
We have brands like I Do,

622
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:34,610
Omega,

623
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:36,210
and other famous brands.

624
00:33:36,300 --> 00:33:38,100
You can see them as you go around.

625
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:39,910
Your main responsibilities are

626
00:33:39,910 --> 00:33:42,330
to monitor the appearance of employees,

627
00:33:42,670 --> 00:33:44,930
staff attendance and cleanliness.

628
00:33:45,550 --> 00:33:47,020
You also need to handle

629
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:48,320
customer disputes,

630
00:33:49,060 --> 00:33:50,910
check the elevators and fire hydrants.

631
00:33:50,910 --> 00:33:52,270
They are actually simple tasks.

632
00:33:52,270 --> 00:33:53,750
It means I have to be responsible

633
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:55,020
for everything here.

634
00:33:55,940 --> 00:33:57,010
Yes.

635
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:59,560
But you don't need to be
too serious about it.

636
00:33:59,580 --> 00:34:01,060
Just make your rounds.

637
00:34:01,150 --> 00:34:03,540
I can't do that. Here at QE,

638
00:34:03,630 --> 00:34:05,290
