639
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:07,460
I think you misunderstood me.

640
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:09,179
You're the son of Mr Duan Sr.

641
00:34:09,270 --> 00:34:11,380
Although he has now retired,

642
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:12,790
he was always very caring towards us

643
00:34:12,790 --> 00:34:14,650
when he was the company director.

644
00:34:15,310 --> 00:34:16,300
Manager.

645
00:34:17,370 --> 00:34:19,290
I hope you can treat me fairly.

646
00:34:19,380 --> 00:34:20,980
If I need teachings,

647
00:34:21,070 --> 00:34:22,340
you have to guide me.

648
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:24,409
I'm here to learn.

649
00:34:28,989 --> 00:34:31,620
You are different from what I thought.

650
00:34:32,110 --> 00:34:33,840
Let's go.
I'll show you around.

651
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:04,050
You are here too.

652
00:36:04,140 --> 00:36:06,570
Xi Xi.
Ding Ding told me

653
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:08,930
you're in charge of the private label.

654
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,180
You've worked hard.

655
00:36:14,210 --> 00:36:15,130
It's nothing.

656
00:36:15,220 --> 00:36:16,940
I'm just doing my work.

657
00:36:17,050 --> 00:36:17,980
Please sit down.

658
00:36:18,030 --> 00:36:19,330
Yes. Take a seat.

659
00:36:20,310 --> 00:36:21,550
Today is the first day of broadcast

660
00:36:21,550 --> 00:36:23,560
for Vine's second season.

661
00:36:23,940 --> 00:36:27,140
Sales are good.
The company is satisfied with the result.

662
00:36:27,300 --> 00:36:28,540
This is a reward

663
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:30,420
that my father appealed for you.

664
00:36:36,070 --> 00:36:37,330
Thank you, Uncle Shen.

665
00:36:37,590 --> 00:36:39,460
You're welcome.

666
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:40,940
This is Ding Ding's first victory

667
00:36:40,940 --> 00:36:43,220
since he joined Rui.

668
00:36:43,420 --> 00:36:46,100
You contributed half of the success.

669
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:48,830
Since this is everyone's hard work,

670
00:36:48,830 --> 00:36:50,030
I want to use this money

671
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:52,310
to continue investing
in the private label.

672
00:36:52,310 --> 00:36:53,900
Work is work.
This reward is personal.

673
00:36:53,900 --> 00:36:55,330
You can keep this money.

674
00:36:56,830 --> 00:36:58,420
We have another matter.

675
00:36:58,620 --> 00:37:01,940
I plan to start a new department

676
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:04,110
to research on and develop private labels.

677
00:37:04,110 --> 00:37:05,570
Vine is not enough.

678
00:37:05,860 --> 00:37:08,030
We have to develop
different private labels

679
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:10,380
to cater to different consumer needs.

680
00:37:10,940 --> 00:37:12,830
You have the most experience in this.

681
00:37:12,830 --> 00:37:14,380
I want you to handle this department.

682
00:37:14,380 --> 00:37:17,100
As for Vine, Yu Shi will take over.

683
00:37:17,580 --> 00:37:19,940
You're obviously undermining me
with this promotion.

684
00:37:19,940 --> 00:37:22,220
You're taking Vine away from me.

685
00:37:35,070 --> 00:37:36,270
Let me brief you on this.

686
00:37:36,270 --> 00:37:38,060
The idea came from Xi Xi.

687
00:37:38,140 --> 00:37:39,900
It's in a form of competition.

688
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:41,700
Broadcasters will be matched
to compete against each other.

689
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:44,050
They'll be given garments randomly.

690
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:45,590
Whom do I match with?

691
00:37:45,620 --> 00:37:46,900
You're your own match.

692
00:37:46,990 --> 00:37:49,180
Nobody wants to compete with a celebrity.

693
00:37:49,180 --> 00:37:51,070
Only after the finals, that winner

694
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:52,270
will compete with you.

695
00:37:52,270 --> 00:37:54,030
This sounds interesting.

696
00:37:54,110 --> 00:37:55,540
Yes, it is.
Since you're now clear about it,

697
00:37:55,540 --> 00:37:56,660
I'll carry on with my work.

698
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:57,650
Alright.

699
00:38:03,750 --> 00:38:04,740
Xi Xi.

700
00:38:07,420 --> 00:38:09,460
What's wrong?

701
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:12,460
Darn it.

702
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:15,890
Why are you here at this time?

703
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:18,330
Now you know I'm crying.

704
00:38:18,750 --> 00:38:20,140
What does it matter?

705
00:38:22,030 --> 00:38:23,330
Wipe your tears.

706
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:29,250
Thanks.

707
00:38:32,310 --> 00:38:35,330
What happened?
Did Ding Ding bully you again?

708
00:38:36,420 --> 00:38:37,560
No.

709
00:38:45,310 --> 00:38:46,700
He wants me

710
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:51,940
to lead a new department.

711
00:38:52,310 --> 00:38:54,770
He's promoting me with a salary increment.

712
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:57,870
But he's actually undermining me.

713
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,770
This is bullying.

714
00:39:02,270 --> 00:39:04,900
So many things happened lately.

715
00:39:06,380 --> 00:39:08,460
I just can't take it.

716
00:39:08,660 --> 00:39:09,860
Alright, alright.

717
00:39:10,350 --> 00:39:12,220
Just let it all out.

718
00:39:12,310 --> 00:39:14,110
You need to let it out sometimes.

719
00:39:14,310 --> 00:39:16,490
-I'm fine.
-Just let it out.

720
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:19,660
I've to take this call.

721
00:39:22,700 --> 00:39:23,970
Hello? Mum?

722
00:39:24,830 --> 00:39:26,010
I have work.

723
00:39:26,410 --> 00:39:28,610
It's the first day of my private label.

724
00:39:30,830 --> 00:39:32,050
What?

725
00:39:32,130 --> 00:39:34,860
Why did you accept the job
without consulting me?

726
00:39:36,110 --> 00:39:38,900
I can't go.
Not today.

727
00:39:39,900 --> 00:39:41,900
I have to go.

728
00:39:44,990 --> 00:39:45,980
What happened?

729
00:39:46,830 --> 00:39:48,290
My mum really amazes me.

730
00:39:48,550 --> 00:39:51,220
It's no use apologising now.
You knocked over my kid.

731
00:39:51,220 --> 00:39:52,620
I didn't do it on purpose.

732
00:39:52,620 --> 00:39:54,330
I didn't see him coming.

733
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:56,220
This is your problem.

734
00:39:56,310 --> 00:39:57,220
Excuse me.

735
00:39:57,310 --> 00:39:59,570
I'm the mall manager.
You can speak to me.

736
00:39:59,860 --> 00:40:01,900
He knocked over my kid.

737
00:40:02,110 --> 00:40:03,330
Look, Mr Manager,

738
00:40:03,460 --> 00:40:04,860
