739
00:40:04,860 --> 00:40:06,310
-Yes, yes.
-This delivery guy

740
00:40:06,310 --> 00:40:08,290
pushes so many parcels around.

741
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:10,830
-It's very dangerous.
-Yes, it's our mistake.

742
00:40:10,830 --> 00:40:12,050
Is your kid alright?

743
00:40:12,180 --> 00:40:13,130
Are you hurt?

744
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:14,570
He was frightened.

745
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:16,140
I'm sorry.
Let me apologise to you.

746
00:40:16,140 --> 00:40:17,130
I'm sorry, kid.

747
00:40:17,830 --> 00:40:20,100
Madam, I have two discount coupons

748
00:40:20,210 --> 00:40:21,410
for the toy shop here.

749
00:40:21,510 --> 00:40:22,910
You can get your kid a toy.

750
00:40:22,990 --> 00:40:24,330
Go buy yourself a toy.

751
00:40:24,420 --> 00:40:25,790
-Say thank you.
-Thank you.

752
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:28,110
-You're welcome.
-I'll let you off this time.

753
00:40:28,110 --> 00:40:29,850
I'm very sorry.

754
00:40:30,030 --> 00:40:31,290
I'm really very sorry.

755
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:33,700
Could you kindly disperse?

756
00:40:33,700 --> 00:40:34,810
Thanks.

757
00:40:36,460 --> 00:40:37,820
I didn't do it on purpose.

758
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:40,180
The kid was running so fast
towards my trolley.

759
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:41,340
I couldn't avoid him.

760
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:42,740
It's okay.
In the future,

761
00:40:42,790 --> 00:40:44,030
