762
00:40:44,030 --> 00:40:45,030
in the security room downstairs.

763
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,790
Our mall doesn't allow deliveries.

764
00:40:46,790 --> 00:40:47,990
I'm here to collect parcels.

765
00:40:47,990 --> 00:40:49,310
A shop called for a collection.

766
00:40:49,310 --> 00:40:50,420
That's why I came up here.

767
00:40:50,420 --> 00:40:51,420
So many?

768
00:40:52,180 --> 00:40:53,980
That's normal for that shop.

769
00:40:54,070 --> 00:40:55,530
I have to make two trips every day.

770
