00:40:57,030 --> 00:40:58,940
This perfume is more subtle.

772
00:40:59,700 --> 00:41:02,230
Hello, Manager Duan.
You can take a seat here.

773
00:41:03,030 --> 00:41:04,570
You're here.
Can I help you?

774
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:05,940
What are you doing?

775
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:07,940
