777
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:10,020
Perfumes.

778
00:41:10,110 --> 00:41:11,570
We have an online shop.

779
00:41:11,660 --> 00:41:13,020
Our manager does live streams

780
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,420
to promote our perfumes.

781
00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:17,030
So the parcels you send out everyday

782
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:18,030
