790
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:33,360
instead of a proper place?

791
00:41:34,660 --> 00:41:35,690
It doesn't matter.

792
00:41:35,690 --> 00:41:36,940
Besides, customers can see

793
00:41:36,940 --> 00:41:38,070
