00:42:01,980 --> 00:42:03,710
Thanks for taking me out today.

804
00:42:04,830 --> 00:42:06,660
I've always wanted to do this.

805
00:42:06,950 --> 00:42:08,940
When Mr Ding joined the company

806
00:42:09,020 --> 00:42:10,810
and you were ousted as the CEO,

807
00:42:10,910 --> 00:42:13,260
I thought of taking you
on a relaxing outing.

808
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,940
But when I saw you

809
00:42:15,030 --> 00:42:16,050
working so hard,

810
00:42:16,270 --> 00:42:18,370
I decided not to disturb you.

811
00:42:19,710 --> 00:42:21,840
Too many things have happened lately.

812
00:42:22,350 --> 00:42:24,700
I just don't know how to deal with it.

813
00:42:24,790 --> 00:42:26,700
I can only occupy myself

