00:42:45,900 --> 00:42:48,070
You're the only one who can protect Vine,

823
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:49,240
Mr Five

824
00:42:49,330 --> 00:42:50,220
and our brand's

825
00:42:50,310 --> 00:42:52,220
original mission.

